title: Hour 3 - Pat Fitzgerald, Will Ferrell
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Pat Fitzgerald, Will Ferrell
description:
Dan Patrick talks with Northwestern HC Pat Fitzgerald joins the show to talk about their big win in Ireland over Nebraska. Fried of the show Will Ferrell calls in to put a cap on the show. Plus, Dan updates you on the latest in Cut Day in the NFL.
